@startuml
!include _yunlink_protocol_theme.iuml
title 会话状态机

state "Discovered" as Discovered <<Neutral>>
state "Handshaking" as Handshaking <<Transit>>
state "Authenticated" as Authenticated <<Transit>>
state "Negotiated" as Negotiated <<Transit>>
state "Active" as Active <<ActiveState>>
state "Draining" as Draining <<Terminal>>
state "Closed" as Closed <<Risk>>

[*] --> Discovered
Discovered --> Handshaking : SessionHello
Handshaking --> Authenticated : SessionAuthenticate success
Handshaking --> Closed : shared_secret mismatch
Authenticated --> Negotiated : SessionCapabilities accepted
Negotiated --> Active : SessionReady + protocol major match
Negotiated --> Closed : capability mismatch\nor major mismatch
Active --> Draining : transport disconnect\nor graceful close
Active --> Closed : explicit close / fatal violation
Draining --> Closed : cleanup complete
Closed --> [*]

note right of Handshaking
前置握手阶段关心的是：
身份建立、认证完成、
是否具备进入控制面的资格。
end note

note bottom of Active
只有 Active 会话才应承载控制类命令。
end note
@enduml
